title: I tried replacing Google with TikTok, and it worked better than I thought
excerpt: TikTok won’t kill Google yet, but it’s a new and fun way to think about search.

title: For Gen Z, TikTok Is the New Search Engine (Published 2022)
excerpt: Need to find a restaurant or figure out how to do something? Young people are turning to TikTok to search for answers. Google has noticed.
